T1  - Can mergers ensure the survival of credit unions in the third millennium?
AU  - Ralston, Deborah
AU  - Wright, April
AU  - Garden, Kaylee
JO  - Journal of Banking & Finance
VL  - 25
IS  - 12
SP  - 2277
EP  - 2304
